# Frontend Flutter

- Share form/grid metadata contract with web client via the same backend schema (`lib/metadata_contract.dart`).
- Entity UX in `lib/app/entity_list_screen.dart` + `entity_record_screen.dart`; shared theme in `lib/theme.dart` (not `main.dart`).
- Dynamic renderers only — no hard-coded entity field layouts.
- `flutter analyze` + `flutter test` run in CI (`client-lint-mobile` job).
